   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support the journey towards justice with education</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Iran Academia plans to deliver the very first open online course (MOOC) in Persian on transitional justice processes. The course targets students from countries with histories of mass atrocities, such as Iran, who are denied access to education on issues related to accountability and truth-seeking. It provides students with the opportunity to learn about judicial and non-judicial mechanisms needed for restoring the dignity of victims and finding durable solutions in fragile societies.</narrative>
  </description>
